下次有急事時，再找我們兩個
Better you call on us only in dire need.

511
00:43:35,545 --> 00:43:38,844
用占卜石自己確定星星的位置
And use your runes to Iocate the star yourself.

512
00:43:39,050 --> 00:43:43,848
