who could've helped me.

529
00:46:34,423 --> 00:46:38,689
翻來覆去地只說「維多利亞這個…那個」
Going on and on and on. Just "Victoria this" and "Victoria that."

530
00:46:41,097 --> 00:46:42,325
特裡斯頓？
Tristan?

531
00:46:43,766 --> 00:46:46,360
請保護我們的妹妹，特裡斯頓
Please protect our sister, Tristan-

532
00:46:47,403 --> 00:46:50,236
亞伊尼正處在危險中
Yvaine is in grave danger-

533
00:46:51,073 --> 00:46:53,371
獨角獸去幫她了
The unicorn came to help her-

534
00:46:54,110 --> 00:46:56,601
但是現在他們正走向一個圈套
But now they're heading into a trap-

535
00:47:00,616 --> 00:47:03,414
在風暴要塞，沒有星星是絕對安全的
No star is safe in Stormhold-

536
00:47:04,353 --> 00:47:08,653
400年前，上個星星墜落了
The last to fall, 400 years ago,

537
00:47:08,758 --> 00:47:10,594
她被女巫捕獲了
was captured by the same witches who seek Yvaine now-

538
00:47:10,618 --> 00:47:14,094
現在尋找亞伊尼的，正是那群女巫

539
00:47:15,298 --> 00:47:16,925
她們欺騙了她
They tricked her,

540
00:47:18,467 --> 00:47:19,957
照顧她
cared for her,

541
00:47:21,270 --> 00:47:24,899
知道她的心再次發光
and when her heart was once more aglow,

542
00:47:25,508 --> 00:47:28,875
然後剖開她的胸膛，把心拿出來
they cut it from her chest

543
00:47:29,946 --> 00:47:31,573
再吃了它
and ate it-

544
00:47:34,150 --> 00:47:36,118
不能再浪費時間了
There's no time to waste-

545
00:47:36,219 --> 00:47:37,948
馬車馬上就來了
A coach is coming-

546
00:47:38,054 --> 00:47:41,683
不管用什麼方法，你一定要坐上去
By any means possible, you must get on it-

547
00:47:42,325 --> 00:47:43,383
快！
Run-

548
00:48:14,323 --> 00:48:15,415
哇！
Whoa!

549
00:48:23,900 --> 00:48:26,892
如果要我送個男孩給他幹活
If Septimus insists on sending a boy to do a man's job...

550
00:48:27,003 --> 00:48:27,992
不，不，不，請等等！
No, no, no, wait, please!

551
00:48:28,104 --> 00:48:29,969
我不認識塞普蒂默斯，只想搭個便車
I don't know a Septimus. I just need a lift.

552
00:48:30,072 --> 00:48:32,870
看看我…我沒武器，求你
Look at me, Iook at me. I'm unarmed. PIease.

553
00:48:33,309 --> 00:48:35,368
求你，讓我和你一起走
PIease, Iet me ride with you.

554
00:48:35,478 --> 00:48:38,845
恐怕不行，我有重要的事情要辦
I'm afraid that's impossible. I'm on a quest of enormous importance.

555
00:48:38,948 --> 00:48:40,848
那你更應該帶上我了
Well, then all the more reason to take me with you.

556
00:48:40,950 --> 00:48:44,442
必要時你會需要多一雙手來幫你，先生？
There may come a time when you need a second pair of hands. Sir?

557
00:48:44,553 --> 00:48:48,882
求你，命運讓我見到你，就向它讓你見到我一樣
PIease. Maybe providence sent me to you just as it sent you to me.

558
00:48:49,625 --> 00:48:52,321
上來　　　哦，好的，謝謝
-Get on. -Oh, yes. Thank you.

559
00:49:17,420 --> 00:49:20,947
天啊，親愛的，外面這麼大雨，進來吧
Goodness me, my dear. Come in out of this wretched rain!

560
00:49:21,390 --> 00:49:23,622
我們有食物和飲料，溫暖的床
We have food and drink, a warm bed and plenty of hot water for a bath.

561
00:49:23,640 --> 00:49:25,622
還提供充足的熱水供你洗澡

562
00:49:44,714 --> 00:49:48,878
你喜歡怎樣洗？溫水，熱水還是沸水？
How do you like your bath? Warm, hot or boil-a-Iobster?

563
00:49:49,819 --> 00:49:51,013
說實話我也不知道
I honestly don't know.

564
00:49:51,120 --> 00:49:52,519
那我來幫你決定吧
Then Iet me choose for you,

565
00:49:52,621 --> 00:49:55,818
我會讓我的丈夫把你的馬帶到馬房裡
and I'll have my husband take your horse to the stable.

566
00:49:56,792 --> 00:49:57,918
比利？
Billy?

567
00:50:08,804 --> 00:50:12,069
現在，我們幫你把濕衣服脫掉好嗎？
Now, Iet's get you out of your wet things, shall we?

568
00:50:23,386 --> 00:50:24,853
感到好些了嗎？
Feeling better?

569
00:50:24,954 --> 00:50:26,683
好多了，謝謝
Much. Thank you.

570
00:50:27,089 --> 00:50:29,580
溫水實際上讓我很舒服
The warm water's actually done me a world of good.

571
00:50:29,692 --> 00:50:32,661
知道了吧？熱水澡的威力就在這兒
You see? The powers of a nice, hot bath.

572
00:50:32,762 --> 00:50:35,196
你的腿部？感覺好些了嗎？
And your Ieg? Any improvement?

573
00:50:37,099 --> 00:50:38,930
棒極了
That is extraordinary.

574
00:50:39,435 --> 00:50:43,166
我只能做些小事，你感到舒服我很高興
It's the very Ieast I could do. I'm just glad you're feeling better.

575
00:50:43,272 --> 00:50:45,137
你看起來也很快樂的樣子
You seem happier in yourself, too.

576
00:50:45,241 --> 00:50:48,540
我確實感到快樂點，煩惱慢慢消失
I do feel happier. Less troubled.

577
00:50:49,779 --> 00:50:50,939
太棒了
Wonderful.

578
00:50:51,347 --> 00:50:54,942
沒有比泡熱水澡更能溫暖你心中的折皺了
Nothing like a nice soak to warm the cockles of your heart.

579
00:51:02,925 --> 00:51:06,258
現在，我只是個旅館主婦
Now, I'm only a simple innkeeper's wife,

580
00:51:06,362 --> 00:51:09,854
但人們說我有一雙可以幫人療養的手
but I've been told I have a healer's hands.

581
00:51:11,000 --> 00:51:13,434
我可以給你按摩
I'd be glad to give you a massage.

582
00:51:13,969 --> 00:51:15,459
按摩是什麼？
What's a massage?

583
00:51:15,571 --> 00:51:18,802
沒試過…上帝啊
Never had... Well, bless my soul.

584
00:51:19,542 --> 00:51:23,672
沒什麼能使你被按摩後那樣，睡得又香又甜
Nothing like a massage to send you off for the finest and deepest night's sleep.

585
00:51:23,779 --> 00:51:25,246
我確實晚上很難入睡
I do have trouble sleeping at night.

586
00:51:25,347 --> 00:51:27,212
躺下吧，親愛的
Lie on your back, dear.

587
00:51:30,252 --> 00:51:32,220
為什麼不閉上眼睛？
Why not close your eyes?

588
00:51:33,289 --> 00:51:35,655
閉上眼睛可以更快入睡
You'll drift off better that way.

589
00:51:50,039 --> 00:51:51,063
有人嗎！
Hello!

590
00:51:53,175 --> 00:51:54,164
需要服務！
Service!

591
00:51:54,276 --> 00:51:56,801
可能我們應該繼續找下一個旅店
Maybe we should carry on and try the next inn,

592
00:51:56,912 --> 00:51:59,642
如果石頭靠近你的羅盤了，更應該這樣
especially if this stone is as close as your runes say.

593
00:51:59,748 --> 00:52:01,477
我再試一次
I'll give it one more try.

594
00:52:06,021 --> 00:52:07,249
放鬆，親愛的
Relax here, my Iove.

595
00:52:07,356 --> 00:52:10,723
我一接待完客人，就馬上回來
I'll be back just as soon as I've taken care of this customer.

596
00:52:15,831 --> 00:52:18,265
終於，我們需要住宿
At Iast. We require accommodation.

597
00:52:18,367 --> 00:52:21,700
