606
00:53:11,287 --> 00:53:12,481
不，不，不，不，不
No, no, no, no, no.

607
00:53:13,389 --> 00:53:14,378
不
No.

608
00:53:15,357 --> 00:53:19,384
在我兄弟死之前，我發誓只喝我自己的酒
Until my brother is dead, I have vowed to drink only my own wine.

609
00:53:21,530 --> 00:53:25,022
我在外面馬房的朋友可能會喝點
Though my friend in the stables might be glad of a drop.

610
00:53:27,336 --> 00:53:29,270
你最好的客房，有嗎？
Your best room, perhaps?

611
00:53:30,873 --> 00:53:32,204
當然
Of course.

612
00:53:39,415 --> 00:53:41,542
對不起，我假定…
I'm sorry. I presumed that...

613
00:53:42,117 --> 00:53:44,085
獨自旅行，是嗎？
Traveling alone, are you?

614
00:53:45,588 --> 00:53:48,955
我剛把四匹公馬和馬車放在馬房裡
I've just stabled my four black stallions and my carriage.

615
00:53:49,058 --> 00:53:52,186
我說我的，他們是我過世的父親的
Well, I say mine. It belonged to my Iate father.

616
00:54:06,175 --> 00:54:07,403
謝謝
Thank you.

617
00:54:07,509 --> 00:54:11,809
你真好，非常感謝，我叫特裡斯頓，你呢？
That's so kind, thank you very much. My name's Tristan. What's yours?

618
00:54:11,914 --> 00:54:13,142
伯納德
Bernard.

619
00:54:20,956 --> 00:54:24,084
沒什麼馬匹或牲畜…他不能駕御的
There was not a horse or beast he could not master.

620
00:54:24,193 --> 00:54:26,923
他年輕時，曾經去騎一頭駱駝
So much so that in his youth, he took to riding a camel,

621
00:54:27,029 --> 00:54:28,394
顯得非常滑稽
which was comical.

622
00:54:28,497 --> 00:54:30,590
他死後，馬車就歸我了
When he passed, the carriage came to me.

623
00:54:30,699 --> 00:54:31,723
她戴著寶石
She's got the stone!

624
00:54:31,834 --> 00:54:32,823
她戴著寶石　　　她戴著寶石
-She's got it! -She's got it!

625
00:54:32,935 --> 00:54:36,200
他們說是要塞裡最大的馬車
And it's the Iargest in all of Stormhold, so they say.

626
