太棒了，失陪一下
How nice for you. If you'll excuse me.

627
00:54:39,174 --> 00:54:40,266
等等
Wait.

628
00:54:40,976 --> 00:54:42,967
你戴著那個寶石，不可能吧
That stone you're wearing. It can't be.

629
00:54:43,078 --> 00:54:44,670
哦，終於…　　是啊，好的，不錯
-Oh, finally. -Yeah, good, well done, yes, sir.

630
00:54:44,780 --> 00:54:45,747
幹得不錯　　　寶貝
-Well done. -Sweet.

631
00:54:45,848 --> 00:54:46,837
過來，讓我看看
Come here. Let me see it.

632
00:54:59,895 --> 00:55:01,886
你根本不明白你動了誰的東西
You have no idea what you're meddling with.

633
00:55:01,997 --> 00:55:04,999
我是普裡默斯，風暴要塞的老大
I am Primus, the first born of Stormhold and I demand that you bring it to me!

634
00:55:05,017 --> 00:55:07,799
我要求你趕快把它給我

635
00:55:07,903 --> 00:55:09,393
把寶石給我，現在就給我！
Bring me the stone! Now!

636
00:55:09,505 --> 00:55:10,633
